\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Decision--theoretic pattern discovery refers to a wide variety of techniques
 that operate, in general, on data which is in vector form.
 These techniques can be divided into three main areas depending on how
 pattern classes are determined: decision functions, distance functions,
 and likelihood functions
\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset citation
